<emphasis id="B93BEAA4FFBC8D24F51CA03B97F7B77F" bold="true" box="[1385,1784,2387,2416]" pageId="2" pageNumber="153">Subspecies and Distribution.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF036B6FFBC8D24F519A01297D1B7B0" blockId="2.[1378,2590,2115,3321]" pageId="2" pageNumber="153">
<taxonomicName id="4C4F4D35FFBC8D24F519A01297EEB798" authority="Thomas, 1920" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1920" box="[1388,1761,2426,2455]" class="Mammalia" family="Calomyscidae" genus="Calomyscus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="2" pageNumber="153" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="baluchi" subSpecies="baluchi">C.b.baluchiThomas,1920—ECAfghanistan(SKoh-i-BabaMts)andWPakistan(NWaziristantoBalochistan).</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
